  "text": "In this paper we compare the data acquired during the 2001-2002 SQ by a long-baseline tiltmeter [CITATION_1] , with data obtained from the nearby permanent GPS station ACAP, to ascertain that the duration of the SQ is twice as long as the apparent active phase of the event.",
